{"tid":811786,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【柒出國際】港5毫當100円入扭蛋機　日店出告示怒斥：非常煩厭","createTime":"2018-09-09T06:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T06:23:18.000Z","uid":206087,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82652512bd518808ef912346d8f0ebe8210e6085","tid":811786,"uid":206087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"販買機和扭蛋機在日本十分常見，但有港人竟利用投幣的漏洞騙財，網上流傳有日本店舖貼出告示，呼籲人們不要以香港5毫硬幣當作100円日元硬幣（約7.07港元）使用，並表明「令人非常煩厭」，不少網民直斥如此騙財的行為無恥，更有人找出過去的報道，表示2004年已有同類型的事件。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一張日本雜貨店自動扭蛋機上的告示，圖中可見當中寫上「Do not use this coin（不准用這硬幣）」，並標示了港幣5毫前、後兩面，又寫上「Very annoying（好煩擾）」，可見店主應該已不止一次「中招」。<br />\n<br />\n根據匯率，100円日元約等於約7.07港元，如果用5毫扭蛋，即足足少付了6.57港元，價錢相差13倍。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/141311_80b1cfb60f03b55a280fd0a3f31e1b4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F141311_80b1cfb60f03b55a280fd0a3f31e1b4d.png&h=775c3527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f207eb3a808fe4a826e8cf503521b40f747311","tid":811786,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"大家都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34a5c19c0c44bca1861e91e415a808aecc88736","tid":811786,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d613f491f13bf3991637b07c7dbaddb2b6105abf","tid":811786,"uid":37856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:21:08.000Z","msg":"原來港5毫同100円既磁通量一樣"},{"pid":"aa19d38c05833dd3a7faa49fab0e99272541ce4c","tid":811786,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"幾蚊都要慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正一大種乞衣<img src=\"/